snippet.title: Awakening Sarah Teaser
snippet.description:
A small teaser showcasing some of the features in Awakening Sarah, the sequel to Dreaming Sarah.

Game by Andre Chagas Silva
Music by Anthony Septim

Full OST now available at https://anthonyseptim.bandcamp.com/album/awakening-sarah-ost

Website: http://asteristic.com
Twitter: http://twitter.com/andreyin
